</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb12176">Mann, Thomas</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02138">Adam an Schnitzler, 15. 5. 1913</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02140">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 5. 7. 1913</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02108">Mann an Schnitzler, 8. 12. 1912</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02270">Mann an Schnitzler, 27. 8. 1917</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
